    "description": "欢迎加入我们的中文讨论组！《孤山速降 Lonely Mountains: Downhill》官方玩家QQ群：535390761<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/711540/extras/e572d6dc46951ed0b4bf231be752c611.avif?t=1765990642\" width=600 height=72 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/711540/extras/1a4dbcc16651800db8f1252e15b5d445.poster.avif?t=1765990642\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/711540/extras/1a4dbcc16651800db8f1252e15b5d445.webm?t=1765990642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/711540/extras/1a4dbcc16651800db8f1252e15b5d445.mp4?t=1765990642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这是你和单车的独享时刻。在自然秀美的山间来一场刺激的下坡之旅。你将穿越茂密的树林、狭窄的山路以及激荡的河流。你可以加速、跳跃、滑行、但尽量别摔倒，从山顶一路冲向山谷吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/711540/extras/d0bad30cebdbdc7a718ab6681b08db2c.webp?t=1765990642\" width=600 height=55 /></span><br>你可以随心所欲一路欣赏山上的美景，也可以挑战计时竞速赛。每座山都有数个不同的坡道，途经静谧的山湖、壮丽的森林以及陡峭的峡谷。游戏拥有量身定制的物理系统，玩家可以小心地在大石块间跳跃，加速飞越深谷或者滑行穿过泥地。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/711540/extras/70b027074343a667dd006a766f016624.avif?t=1765990642\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/711540/extras/6f84ed0f786907eadd119561f0598220.webp?t=1765990642\" width=600 height=55 /></span><br>一切随你！你可以走轻松的观光路线，也可以脱离道路，找出一条通往终点线的最快路径！快快掌握游戏紧凑而灵敏的操作手感，发掘隐藏的休憩点以及秘密捷径。这里既没有观众，也没有护栏警示带，只有未被人类破坏的自然美景。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/711540/extras/8f03631d6187618ae989d93fd58c0684.avif?t=1765990642\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/711540/extras/4b4bfe88e6e86594022d4ecc0e031472.webp?t=1765990642\" width=600 height=55 /></span><br>快来解锁新的难度模式，站上排行榜证明你的竞速天赋吧！你需要夜以继日地磨练技巧，最后才能在危险重重的“自由竞速”模式中和全世界最棒的骑手们一教高下！每辆单车的操作手感都有区别，尽快找到最适合你操作风格的那一辆，从山上飞驰而下吧。还有数十种单车涂装和人物服装等你来解锁！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/711540/extras/a0305a9c748a3f5c9a3bd108ef4f0d62.avif?t=1765990642\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/711540/extras/1e71a09590e86249bdd615bd704d606d.avif?t=1765990642\" width=600 height=914 /></span><br><br>欢迎加入我们的中文讨论组！《孤山速降 Lonely Mountains: Downhill》官方玩家QQ群：535390761",
